ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-Spain Protocol amending the Convention for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada the Protocol between Canada and the KINGDOM OF SPAIN amending the CONVENTION for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital, signed at Ottawa on November 23, 1976.
